setup steps

* install Ubuntu
* append this to /etc/sudoers:
    kevan ALL=(ALL) NOPASSWD: ALL
* apt install redshift i3 rofi alacritty tmux neovim tldr git git-delta build-essential clang
* curl --proto '=https' --tlsv1.2 -sSf https://sh.rustup.rs | sh
* cargo install jj-cli ripgrep fd-find
* install and configure keyd

* set up ssh keys
* clone this repo
* run update_configs
* log out and back in

* uninstall snap
* download & install chrome
    * load blank new tab page extension
* download & install vs code

* change grub timeout to 2 seconds
* if you're dual-booting windows:
    timedatectl set-local-rtc 1
